rows.label: qst700604_msg0004
rows.name:
Didn't you hear the explanation? It's
a smokescreen, to attract bugs.

rows.label: qst700604_msg0005
rows.name: Ugh... It smells kind of fishy...

rows.label: qst700604_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey!? Why are so many
monsters coming out!?

rows.label: qst700604_msg0007
rows.name:
Hmm, it seems the smokescreen
attracted monsters instead of bugs.

rows.label: qst700604_msg0008
rows.name:
What's with that!?
What a piece of junk!

rows.label: qst700604_msg0009
rows.name:
We can talk later! First, let's
take care of these guys!
